Daniel Libeskind, architect of the 
World Trade Center site, says the new construction at the site 
will be the "center of Manhattan." Libeskind talks with 
Bloomberg's  Tom Keene  and Sara Eisen on Bloomberg Radio's 
"Bloomberg Surveillance."     (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 06:40
 